#. Tag: title
#: help.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "Help &krusader;"
msgstr "सहायता & क्रूसेडर;"

#. Tag: primary
#: help.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "Help"
msgstr "साहाय्यम्‌"

#. Tag: para
#: help.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here is your opportunity to <ulink url=\"https://krusader.org/get-involved/"
"index.html\">contribute</ulink> to the &krusader; project. There are things "
"that need to be done, but cannot be done by us. If you feel you can help, do "
"not hesitate to contact us; every OpenSource can use some help. Please also "
"check the <ulink url=\"https://krusader.org/get-involved/index.html"
"\">contribute</ulink> donate &URL; page on our website for more recent "
"information. Thanks!"
msgstr ""
"अत्र भवतः <ulink url=\"https://krusader.org/get-involved/index.html\">योगदानं</"
"ulink> कर्तुं &krusader; प्रकल्प। तत्र कार्याणि सन्ति, परन्तु अस्माभिः कर्तुं न शक्यन्ते। यदि "
"भवान् मन्यते यत् भवान् साहाय्यं कर्तुं शक्नोति तर्हि अस्माभिः सह सम्पर्कं कर्तुं मा संकोचयतु; "
"प्रत्येकं OpenSource किञ्चित् सहायतां उपयोक्तुं शक्नोति। कृपया <ulink url=\"https://"
"krusader.org/get-involved/index.html\">योगदान</ulink> दानं &URL; पृष्ठे अस्माकं "
"जालपुटे अधिकाधिकं नवीनतमसूचनाः प्राप्तुं शक्नुवन्ति। धन्यवादा!"

#. Tag: para
#: help.docbook:18
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To get contributor account and commit changes to &krusader; by yourselves "
#| "you should follow <ulink url=\"https://community.kde.org/Infrastructure/"
#| "Get_a_Developer_Account\">this tutorial</ulink>. Some useful advices on "
#| "using &kde; Git can be found <ulink url=\"https://community.kde.org/"
#| "Infrastructure/Git\">here</ulink>. It is a good practice to use <ulink "
#| "url=\"https://invent.kde.org/utilities/krusader/-/merge_requests\">merge "
#| "requests</ulink> for the non-trivial patches."
msgid ""
"To get contributor account and commit changes to &krusader; by yourselves "
"you should follow <ulink url=\"https://community.kde.org/Infrastructure/"
"Get_a_Developer_Account\">this tutorial</ulink>. Some useful advice on using "
"&kde; Git can be found <ulink url=\"https://community.kde.org/Infrastructure/"
"Git\">here</ulink>. It is a good practice to use <ulink url=\"https://invent."
"kde.org/utilities/krusader/-/merge_requests\">merge requests</ulink> for the "
"non-trivial patches."
msgstr ""
"योगदानकर्ता खातं प्राप्तुं परिवर्तनं च &krusader; स्वयमेव भवन्तः <ulink url=\"https://"
"community.kde.org/Infrastructure/Get_a_Developer_Account\">एतत् पाठ्यक्रमं</"
"ulink> अनुसरणं कुर्वन्तु । &kde; Git <ulink url=\"https://community.kde.org/"
"Infrastructure/Git\">अत्र</ulink> प्राप्यते । अतुच्छपैचस्य कृते <ulink url=\"https://"
"invent.kde.org/utilities/krusader/-/merge_requests\">विलय-अनुरोध</ulink> "
"इत्यस्य उपयोगः उत्तमः अभ्यासः अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: help.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid "Documentation"
msgstr "दस्तावेजीकरणम्"

#. Tag: para
#: help.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Help is needed (we are looking for documentation writers) for keeping the "
"&krusader; documentation up to date. The draft explanation of new features "
"is done by the developers on the <ulink url=\"https://groups.google.com/"
"group/krusader-devel\">krusader-devel mailing list</ulink>, but we need "
"editors to add this information in the handbook. By playing with the new "
"features these editors can give valuable information to the developers for "
"making the new features even better!"
msgstr ""
"&krusader; अद्यतनं दस्तावेजीकरणं। नूतनविशेषतानां मसौदाव्याख्यानं <ulink url=\"https://"
"groups.google.com/group/krusader-devel\">krusader-devel मेलसूची</ulink> इत्यत्र "
"विकासकैः क्रियते, परन्तु अस्माकं सम्पादकानां आवश्यकता वर्तते एतां सूचनां हस्तपुस्तिकायां "
"योजयन्तु। नूतनविशेषताभिः सह क्रीडन् एते सम्पादकाः नूतनविशेषताः अपि उत्तमं कर्तुं विकासकान् "
"बहुमूल्यं सूचनां दातुं शक्नुवन्ति!"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: help.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bug triaging"
msgstr "बग ट्रायजिंग"

#. Tag: para
#: help.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sometimes bugs are not well reported, that can be mended. In order to free "
"developers, so that they can have more time to &eg; improve &krusader;'s "
"source code and add features: bug reports can be confirmed, or closed. A "
"list of steps to repeat the problem can be made. Some potential causes can "
"be discarded."
msgstr ""
"कदाचित् दोषाः सम्यक् न निवेदिताः, तस्य संशोधनं कर्तुं शक्यते। विकासकान् मुक्तं कर्तुं, येन तेषां "
"&eg; &krusader; इत्यस्य स्रोतसङ्केतं सुधारयन्तु तथा च विशेषताः योजयन्तु: दोषप्रतिवेदनानि "
"पुष्टयितुं, अथवा बन्दं कर्तुं शक्यन्ते। समस्यायाः पुनरावृत्त्यर्थं पदानां सूचीं कर्तुं शक्यते । केचन "
"सम्भाव्यकारणानि परित्यक्तुं शक्यन्ते ।"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: help.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid "Code testing"
msgstr "कोड परीक्षण"

#. Tag: para
#: help.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Before a new &krusader; release is made... many testers are needed to report "
"or confirm problems. If you like to be on the cutting edge of &krusader;, "
"and help by the way, consider reporting!"
msgstr ""
"एकस्य नूतनस्य &krusader; release is made... समस्यानां सूचनां दातुं वा पुष्टयितुं वा बहवः "
"परीक्षकाः आवश्यकाः सन्ति। यदि भवान् &krusader;-इत्यस्य अत्याधुनिक-धारे भवितुं रोचते, तथा "
"च वैसे सहायतां कर्तुं रोचते, तर्हि रिपोर्ट्-करणं कर्तुं विचारयतु!"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: help.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding comments"
msgstr "टिप्पणीं योजयन्"

#. Tag: para
#: help.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are reading &krusader;'s source code, and you think that adding "
"comments is a good idea, that's welcome! It's very probable that your "
"comments will save time to someone else later, accelerating &krusader;'s "
"development."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् &krusader; इत्यस्य स्रोतसङ्केतं पठति, तथा च भवान् मन्यते यत् टिप्पणीं योजयितुं "
"उत्तमः विचारः अस्ति, तर्हि तस्य स्वागतम्! अतीव सम्भाव्यते यत् भवतः टिप्पण्याः पश्चात् "
"अन्यस्य कृते समयस्य रक्षणं करिष्यन्ति, &krusader;"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: help.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tutorial writing"
msgstr "ट्यूटोरियल लेखन"

#. Tag: para
#: help.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tutorials are very useful for people who are starting to use a program, like "
"&krusader;."
msgstr ""
"ये जनाः कार्यक्रमस्य उपयोगं आरभन्ते, तेषां कृते पाठ्यक्रमाः अतीव उपयोगिनो भवन्ति, यथा "
"&krusader;."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: help.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid "English texts reviewing"
msgstr "आङ्ग्लग्रन्थ समीक्षा"

#. Tag: para
#: help.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you can review English texts, and spot writing mistakes, your comments "
"are welcome!"
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् आङ्ग्लग्रन्थानां समीक्षां कर्तुं शक्नोति, लेखनदोषान् च द्रष्टुं शक्नोति तर्हि भवतां "
"टिप्पणीनां स्वागतं भवति!"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: help.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "Solve doubts about &krusader;"
msgstr "&krusader विषये संशयानां समाधानं कुरुत;"

#. Tag: para
#: help.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some &krusader; users can write about their doubts, &eg; in mailing lists. "
"Solving their doubts is very valuable!"
msgstr ""
"केचन &krusader; उपयोक्तारः स्वसंशयानां विषये लिखितुं शक्नुवन्ति, &eg; मेलसूचीषु । तेषां "
"संशयानां समाधानं अतीव मूल्यवान् अस्ति!"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: help.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "&krusader; Extensions"
msgstr "&krusader; विस्तारः"

#. Tag: para
#: help.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please upload your favourite extensions at <ulink url=\"https://store.kde."
"org/\">store.kde.org</ulink>, so that they become available for the "
"&krusader; community. Maybe they will be shipped by default with &krusader; "
"at the next release :-))."
msgstr ""
"कृपया स्वस्य प्रियविस्तारान् <ulink url=\"https://store.kde.org/\">store.kde.org</"
"ulink> इत्यत्र अपलोड् कुर्वन्तु, येन ते &krusader; समुदाय। कदाचित् ते पूर्वनिर्धारितरूपेण "
"&krusader; अग्रिमे विमोचनसमये :-))."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: help.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spread the Word &krusader;"
msgstr "वाचं प्रसारयतु &krusader;"

#. Tag: para
#: help.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you like &krusader;, let people know! Write articles and reviews for "
"internet or print publications. Encourage your friends to give &krusader; a "
"try. Participate in forums to help others in the community."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवतः &krusader; रोचते तर्हि जनान् ज्ञापयन्तु! अन्तर्जालस्य अथवा मुद्रितप्रकाशनस्य "
"लेखाः समीक्षाः च लिखन्तु। मित्राणि दातुं प्रोत्साहयन्तु &krusader; a try. समुदाये अन्येषां "
"साहाय्यार्थं मञ्चेषु भागं गृह्णन्तु।"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: help.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "&GUI; Translations"
msgstr "&GUI; अनुवादाः"

#. Tag: para
#: help.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&krusader; is available in many languages, but sometimes translations do "
"need an update or translations to new languages are always welcome. If you "
"are interested in translating the &krusader; &GUI;, please contact the "
"<ulink url=\"https://l10n.kde.org/teams-list.php\">&kde; translation team</"
"ulink> of your language."
msgstr ""
"&krusader; बहुषु भाषासु उपलभ्यते, परन्तु कदाचित् अनुवादानाम् अद्यतनस्य आवश्यकता भवति अथवा "
"नूतनासु भाषासु अनुवादस्य सदैव स्वागतं भवति । यदि भवन्तः &krusader; &GUI;, कृपया <ulink "
"url=\"https://l10n.kde.org/teams-list.php\">&kde; भवतः भाषायाः अनुवाददल</"
"ulink>।"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: help.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "Documentation Translations"
msgstr "दस्तावेजीकरण अनुवाद"

#. Tag: para
#: help.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are interested in translating this &krusader; documentation, please "
"contact the <ulink url=\"https://l10n.kde.org/teams-list.php\">&kde; "
"translation team</ulink> of your language."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् एतस्य अनुवादं कर्तुं रुचिं लभते &krusader; दस्तावेजीकरणं, कृपया <ulink url="
"\"https://l10n.kde.org/teams-list.php\">&kde; भवतः भाषायाः अनुवाददल</ulink>।"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: help.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid "Donations"
msgstr "दानं"

#. Tag: para
#: help.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Actually, we had not considered donations, until users asked us for a way to "
"<ulink url=\"https://sourceforge.net/project/project_donations.php?"
"group_id=6488\">Donate</ulink> to the project. &krusader; is, and always "
"will be free, in all the terms of the GNU Public License."
msgstr ""
"वस्तुतः अस्माभिः दानस्य विषये विचारः न कृतः आसीत्, यावत् उपयोक्तारः अस्मान् परियोजनायाः "
"<ulink url=\"https://sourceforge.net/project/project_donations.php?"
"group_id=6488\">दानं</ulink> कर्तुं मार्गं न पृष्टवन्तः &krusader; अस्ति, सर्वदा च मुक्तं "
"भविष्यति, GNU सार्वजनिकानुज्ञापत्रस्य सर्वेषु शर्तेषु ।"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: help.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid "Packagers"
msgstr "संकुलकर्ता"

#. Tag: para
#: help.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"We are always in need of packagers for different distro rpm's, deb's, &etc; "
"All help is welcome."
msgstr ""
"अस्माकं सर्वदा भिन्न-भिन्न distro rpm's, deb's, &etc; सर्वेषां साहाय्यस्य स्वागतम् अस्ति।"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: help.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>FAQ</emphasis>"
msgstr "<emphasis>FAQ</emphasis> इति"

#. Tag: para
#: help.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have a question that is missing in the <link linkend=\"faq\">FAQ</"
"link>, we would like to hear it."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवतः कश्चन प्रश्नः अस्ति यः अत्र लुप्तः अस्ति<link linkend=\"faq\"> FAQ</link> , "
"वयं तत् श्रोतुम् इच्छामः।"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: help.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rate &krusader;"
msgstr "दर & crusader;"

#. Tag: para
#: help.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On some websites you can rate software, if you like &krusader; go to one of "
"these sites and rate &krusader;, thanks."
msgstr ""
"केषुचित् जालपुटेषु भवान् सॉफ्टवेयरस्य मूल्याङ्कनं कर्तुं शक्नोति, यदि भवान् &krusader; एतेषु "
"कस्मिंश्चित् साइट् गत्वा &krusader;, धन्यवादः ।"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: help.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid "Others"
msgstr "अन्ये"

#. Tag: para
#: help.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"faqg_wish\">Feedback</link>, <link linkend=\"faqg_bug_report"
"\">Bug reports</link>, patches, &etc; are always welcome! An open source "
"project's greatest strength is derived from getting user feedback."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"faqg_wish\">स्पर्शावबोध</link> , ९.<link linkend="
"\"faqg_bug_report\"> बग रिपोर्ट् करोति</link> , पट्टिकाः, इत्यादयः; सदैव स्वागतं "
"कुर्वन्ति! मुक्तस्रोतप्रकल्पस्य सर्वाधिकं बलं उपयोक्तृप्रतिक्रियाप्राप्त्यैव प्राप्यते ।"
